  "section": "2.2: Barbarian fishing, Green dragons and the Hallowed Sepulchre",
  "stepText": "Swap to the standard spellbook. Use your Fremennik boots to get to Rellekka. Do The Fremennik Isles (make a Fremennik shield, ‘Neitiznot shield’, along the way for the diary), putting the XP on attack (or defence if you are already level 60). Turn 5 mithril bars into 75 mithril nails at the Jatiszo anvils during the quest. Make a silvthrill rod at the Neitiznot furnace. Enchant your silvthrill rod. Sell your berserker helm back to Skulgrimen after you’ve obtained the Helm of Neitiznot.\n",
